libBarcodes â€” static library which summarizes all efforts of the barcode scanning for iOS
under the unified single umbrella controller

Some work derived & base ideas of scan controller are borrowed from CardIO library, by
the courtesy of eBay Software Foundation. see below for more info

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scanning
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

libBarcodes aggregates three ways of barcode scanning with 3rd party components:

 * iOS system approach (iOS7+)
 * ZXing (used ZXingObjC port)
 * ZBar (curtsy to ultrafast and stable library ever)

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Generating
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

At this moment libBarcodes uses ZXingObjC to generate barcodes

